lead_paragraph: West Indies reached 114-5 against Pakistan with inspirational opener Kraigg Brathwaite still at the crease after a tense fourth day ended early due to bad light as they chased a victory target of 153 in the third test in Sharjah on Wednesday.

headline.print_headline: Brilliant Brathwaite Takes West Indies to the Brink
